--Load GS data to HDFS
--First create a new Hive table(wdi_csv_text)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS wdi_csv_text
(year INTEGER, countryName STRING, countryCode STRING, indicatorName STRING, indicatorCode STRING, 
indicatorValue FLOAT)
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY ',' LINES TERMINATED BY '\n'
LOCATION 'hdfs:///user/yashar/hive/wdi/wdi_csv_text'

--INSERT query to load data from wdi_gs to wdi_csv_text
INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE wdi_csv_text
SELECT * FROM wdi_gs
SELECT COUNT(countryName) AS count FROM wdi_csv_text

-- CREATE TABLE using OpenCSVSerde
CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE IF NOT EXISTS wdi_opencsv_gs
(year INTEGER, countryName STRING, countryCode STRING, indicatorName STRING, indicatorCode STRING,indicatorValue FLOAT)
ROW FORMAT SERDE 'org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.OpenCSVSerde'
WITH SERDEPROPERTIES (
   "separatorChar" = ",",
   "quoteChar"     = "\"",
   "escapeChar"    = "\\"
)
LOCATION 'gs://jarvis_data_eng_yashar/datasets/wdi_2016'

SELECT DISTINCT (indicatorCode) FROM wdi_opencsv_gs
ORDER BY indicatorCode 
limit 20

CREATE VIEW IF NOT EXISTS wdi_opencsv_text_view AS 
SELECT cast(year AS INTEGER), countryName, countryCode,indicatorName,indicatorCode,cast(indicatorValue AS FLOAT)
FROM wdi_opencsv_text

-- Query to find out correct indicator name/code
SELECT DISTINCT (indicatorCode), indicatorName
FROM wdi_opencsv_text
WHERE indicatorCode LIKE '%GDP%'

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS wdi_opencsv_text_partitions
(countryName STRING, countryCode STRING, 
  indicatorName STRING, indicatorCode STRING, 
  indicatorValue FLOAT
) PARTITIONED BY(year INTEGER)
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED 
LOCATION 'hdfs:///user/yashar/hive/wdi/wdi_opencsv_text_partitions'

set hive.exec.dynamic.partition.mode=nonstrict;
INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE wdi_opencsv_text_partitions PARTITION (year)
SELECT countryname,
       countrycode,
       indicatorname,
       indicatorcode,
       indicatorvalue,
       year
FROM wdi_opencsv_text;

SELECT year, countryName, indicatorValue
FROM wdi_opencsv_text_partitions
WHERE year = '2015' AND countryName ='Canada' AND indicatorCode = 'NY.GDP.MKTP.KD.ZG'

       year,

paragraphs.text:
-- FIND the highest GDP growth year for each country 
-- using default Hive interpreter
SELECT wdi_csv_parquet.indicatorValue AS value, wdi_csv_parquet.countryName AS country,
wdi_csv_parquet.year AS year
FROM (SELECT MAX(indicatorValue) AS ind, countryName
        FROM wdi_csv_parquet
        WHERE indicatorCode = 'NY.GDP.MKTP.KD.ZG'
            AND indicatorValue <> 0
            GROUP BY countryName) t1
INNER JOIN wdi_csv_parquet
ON t1.ind = wdi_csv_parquet.indicatorValue
    AND t1.countryName = wdi_csv_parquet.countryName

%spark.sql
SELECT wdi_csv_parquet.indicatorValue AS value, wdi_csv_parquet.countryName AS country,
wdi_csv_parquet.year AS year
FROM (SELECT MAX(indicatorValue) AS ind, countryName
        FROM wdi_csv_parquet
        WHERE indicatorCode = 'NY.GDP.MKTP.KD.ZG'
            AND indicatorValue <> 0
            GROUP BY countryName) t1
INNER JOIN wdi_csv_parquet
ON t1.ind = wdi_csv_parquet.indicatorValue
    AND t1.countryName = wdi_csv_parquet.countryName

-- Query that returns GDP growth for all countries
-- Sort By countryName and Year
SELECT countryName, year, indicatorCode
FROM wdi_csv_parquet
WHERE indicatorCode = 'NY.GDP.MKTP.KD.ZG'
DISTRIBUTE BY countryName
SORT BY countryName, year
LIMIT 20
